Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:48.65,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:53.30,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Leave Cal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:57.30,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:01:59.16,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:02.81,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to work out a plan for our escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:05.70,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Our time is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:08.55,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to waste our time on Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:11.31,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:13.30,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you this before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:17.32,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really have the determination to shoot her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:20.78,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:28.83,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:33.84,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some time to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:42.33,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.35,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,But make your decision by today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.63,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't decide...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:52.86,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,...then I'll take care of Drei myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:00.88,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:03.87,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,...save Mio, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:21.04,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let Elen shoot Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.50,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,I have to settle it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.47,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,No one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:27.89,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:29.81,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.39,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:35.45,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:37.71,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.65,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Want to eat lunch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:46.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're basically handcuffed to Mio.\NYou don't really get a chance to eat lunch with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:49.05,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have a lonely table today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:51.40,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,since both Mio and Elen are absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.21,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Elen is absent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.67,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,We both got to school this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.28,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,She left early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:00.80,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wasn't feeling well since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.63,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't notice it at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:05.37,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:06.13,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:08.83,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me how far along you've gotten with Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:21.78,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Elen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:27.82,Default,Oper,0000,0000,0000,,The person you are trying to reach is currently not available. Please hang up and try-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:29.89,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.00,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Quit running and tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:32.79,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How far along have you gotten with-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:34.15,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:34.92,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.77,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What's the rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:39.34,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Are you {\i1}that{\i0} worried about Elen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You've got quite a sister complex-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.56,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:45.26,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,5th period is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:46.51,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:47.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:49.59,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:00.63,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,"Keep your phone off during class."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's called common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.71,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's get back to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.33,Default,Oper,0000,0000,0000,,This is the voicemail system.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.85,Default,Oper,0000,0000,0000,,You have one new message.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:20.54,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,You might be angry by the time you hear this message.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:22.54,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:24.94,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is the best choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:29.92,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't fight Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:35.36,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who dragged Mio into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:39.12,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save her, even if it costs me my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:40.70,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:43.18,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to go ahead and escape without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:48.07,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch up with you after I rescue Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:50.07,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:55.09,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,If by any chance, I don't make it by the appointed time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:06:01.07,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,Think of me as dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:05.90,Default,Oper,0000,0000,0000,,Message received today, at 2:15 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.19,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.84,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Elen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:19.06,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose anyone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.56,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand to see anyone get hurt again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:25.78,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,No one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:35.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Ein...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:38.14,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Our prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:40.25,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We must contact Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:47.74,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:54.10,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,I was expecting you to wail and put up a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:58.10,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:05.67,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,You were completely fooled by that guy, which is why you're here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.78,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be surprised if you looked bitter about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:11.11,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Are you bitter yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.30,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,That you were-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:19.30,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Talking shit now, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:25.68,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:29.63,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,That someone could carry this much hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:33.48,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only one who had to endure sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:35.42,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Reiji also-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:38.71,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,What do {\i1}you{\i0} know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.43,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:42.78,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I wouldn't be able to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:47.17,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Because I truly love him with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:05.14,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.67,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.94,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,You, Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:12.50,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,You're all liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.65,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the same for everyone from this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:24.56,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever shivered from the cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:28.40,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever gotten the crap beaten out of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:34.78,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever survived without eating for three days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:44.51,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:50.69,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think that nothing in this world can hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:56.10,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,You've been treated like a princess your entire life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:58.68,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think everyone lives like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:01.28,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,In a foolish country like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:05.19,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,What would a pampered bitch like you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.68,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:11.86,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know the pain of others...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:13.74,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:14.96,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:20.33,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,I only had one outfit to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:24.33,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,And that one burned to a crisp, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:30.46,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,What did you eat growing up to get such smooth skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.09,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:33.55,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:36.16,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.66,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,...the meaning of true despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:46.60,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling of being powerless and unable to fight back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:49.32,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,I'll engrave it into your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.53,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,A deep scar on your heart that will be with you for the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:54.73,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,I waited here for you... for such a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:24.37,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Because you promised me you'd come back, no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.66,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,I waited...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:30.29,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,...for such a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:35.28,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,For a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.71,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:18.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Shiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:23.01,Default,Shiga,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:27.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you have bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:30.03,Default,Shiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Fujieda Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:36.04,Default,Shiga,0000,0000,0000,,Because of my inattentiveness, your daughter has been dragged into a bit of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:41.55,Default,Shiga,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, we haven't got a minute to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:46.28,Default,Shiga,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that I'm to take full responsibility for the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:51.22,Default,Shiga,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, I believe rescuing Mio is of higher priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:56.77,Default,Shiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm requesting that we dispatch the Godoh Group's retainers to settle the conflict-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:12:00.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is it those Americans who are behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:05.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mio still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.33,Default,Shiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We are sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:10.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it's best not to meddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:13.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use the Godoh Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:17.71,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let those foreigners take care of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.13,Default,Shiga,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:24.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If the Group gets involved, the entire nation will know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:30.71,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,"Why is the Godoh Group getting so worked up over one girl?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:33.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's what everyone will think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:38.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't intend to make you take full responsibility for it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.41,Default,Shiga,0000,0000,0000,,But then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:42.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that there's no need, Shiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:47.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no connection between the Godoh and the Fujieda. There mustn't be one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:52.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Even now... and even in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:54.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Do I make myself clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:58.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Mio's life isn't in danger, do not take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:03.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they're not after money or trying to blackmail us, there's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:07.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But I do appreciate you looking out for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:15.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Shiga, in the end, Yakuza are just useless good-for-nothings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:18.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when it comes to protecting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:23.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Swords and guns are only good for destroying and killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:26.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They can't protect anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.66,Default,Shiga,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.74,Default,Shiga,0000,0000,0000,,I will keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:41.01,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,I've been acting as myself, within the repertoire that I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:48.93,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,That repertoire, that play... has changed its colors, and is nearing its end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:52.52,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,The creation of the ultimate soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:55.48,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,The first creation was Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:58.94,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,And the experimental creations were Zwei and Drei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:05.22,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,By using the results of those experiments, the performers best suited for the final act have been created...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:10.80,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,Zahlenschwestern.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:13.87,Default-Alt,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Note: "Zahlenschwestern" means "number sisters" in German
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.86,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,They have no fear. They know no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:18.50,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,Automatons who carry death like faithful hounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:25.76,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,Both the Godoh Group and Inferno are nothing but stage props.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:33.44,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,When Ein and Zwei, who have been driven into a tight corner by Drei, bare their fangs like the beasts they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:37.93,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,The dream contest between my works of art will commence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:43.94,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,I want you Zahlenschwestern to participate in that contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:47.59,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:54.03,Default,Scythe,0000,0000,0000,,Until we hear the closing chimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.03,Default-Alt,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Ein?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:40.66,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,Drei, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:42.18,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:46.04,Default-Alt,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Pick a place where we won't have any interferences.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:49.67,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put an end to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:54.05,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.36,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:57.73,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.00,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,My... phone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:05.06,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she's talking to Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:08.08,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. That place sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.07,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Three in the morning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:14.97,Default-Alt,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about the ruins that are above Shinokura Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:17.33,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,The place that used to be the girl's dormitory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.83,Default-Alt,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:21.06,Default-Alt,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,That's where Mio is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:24.52,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better prepare something for her to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.60,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.08,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget this ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:55.74,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,It's not worth it to hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:17:02.24,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you choose to, there are tons of people who hate me, and would refuse to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:10.17,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt I'll live for long, and when my time comes, I'll go to hell for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:13.38,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:36.71,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:41.08,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you? I was worried sick-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:45.25,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mio's classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:49.51,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,She was absent from school today, so I brought her assignments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:51.83,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Mio wasn't at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.14,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Please give this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.02,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:57.11,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.65,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:00.93,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:13.21,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:14.19,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:16.14,Default,Zwei,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.95,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:31.99,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Elen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:33.46,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.90,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reason to lie to you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:40.53,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,So... just call me Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:45.97,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Lie? What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:48.56,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.74,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:51.27,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you to...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:52.96,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,Drei did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.07,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Drei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:57.22,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about... Cal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:19:00.11,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,She used to be called that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:02.94,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are you guys...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:05.29,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,You heard from Drei, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:07.71,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:11.96,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Are you and Reiji really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:13.86,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:15.92,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,We're assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.04,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.12,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:23.18,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you go home on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:25.68,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,You can call the police with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:28.18,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:31.54,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Cal left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:36.19,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,She mentioned something about "putting an end to everything".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.55,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's going to kill Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:41.25,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.37,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:45.70,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Then... that phone call from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.58,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to fight her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:55.42,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there... Isn't there something I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:58.17,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I love Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:03.25,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I would do anything for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.83,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Is that not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.67,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Can I not stay by his side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.53,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings for him may very well be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:16.09,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,But those feelings alone are not enough to defeat Drei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:22.00,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't kill her, she'll kill Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:27.53,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,The one who shall prevent that isn't you... but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:33.47,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,If you really want to help Reiji, stay here for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:37.75,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, the likelihood of Reiji surviving will increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:40.05,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.93,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Did Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.26,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:49.68,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who involved you in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:54.88,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji isn't someone who can put on a crying or laughing facade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:21:00.26,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,If you happened to have seen his smile or his tears before,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:03.26,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,they were real.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:20.64,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you called me Elen,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:25.48,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,I've existed for the sole purpose of protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.98,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:29.51,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to continue living...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:47.63,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,If you survive... that's proof that I lived, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:52.67,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:55.19,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,...ghosts that cannot exist anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:58.64,Default,Ein,0000,0000,0000,,We are phantoms with no identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:29.76,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, even if it's in my dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:32.76,Default,Cal,0000,0000,0000,,...can't I at least have a miraculous redemption?
